snippet.textDisplay: When i saw this episode for the first time, i had hear Rahat sahib earlier but i hadnt heard Amjad Sabri sahib and i became an instant fan, His voice, style and smile, what a charming personality!!. I have lost count how many times i have seen this video to hear this once in a life time jugalbandi, especailly to see and hear Sabri sahib. It is my favourite from Coke studio till date. What a colossal loss and sadness i felt hearing the passing of Amjad sahib for the world, south east asia, Pakistan and India. I am from India and i am big fan of Coke Studio Pakistan as everyone i know in India is. May Amjad sahib find peace.
